      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"next chapter\" feels so empty though. Like, what's the point of writing a story when the most important character is gone? It just feels exhausting... like I'm just performing these daily rituals for no one. Every day is just more of the same emptiness, and I'm so tired of fighting it.",
