      "content": "it's just hard to see the point in \"becoming\" someone else when the person i was was so much happier. i feel like i'm just dragging this heavy body around a house that doesn't belong to me anymore. sometimes i just look at the empty side of the bed and think... if i wasn't here, the silence wouldn't be so lonely. it would just be... still.",
